				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/Canh-Tu%E1%BA%A5t-ni%C3%AAn-ch%E1%BA%BF/poem-x1HY9Hmqz-E6-xMz9JnWwA">Canh Tuất niên chế - 庚戌年製</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Khoan/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-T%E1%BB%AD-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF-qu%C3%A2n-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-p5pgcQH9hIJd7vOjcneu2A">Đề Tử Đồng đế quân miếu - 題梓潼帝君廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Khoan/author-Pf4dpRXbHmTjs-pG65imRA">Phùng Khắc Khoan</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/%C4%90%C3%B4ng-Pha-b%C3%A1t-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-yIfDITNcorK2USQnKemVmQ">Đông Pha bát thủ kỳ 3 - 東坡八首其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Nam-tr%C3%AC/poem-1SAz4IPXlcjehpcf2UezrA">Nam trì - 南池</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Qu%E1%BB%B3-ph%E1%BB%A7-th%C6%B0-ho%C3%A0i-t%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-9H3m3-SmgiHr-h2Si7rIvg">Quỳ phủ thư hoài tứ thập vận - 夔府書懷四十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tam-Xuy%C3%AAn-quan-thu%E1%BB%B7-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-dYBU0BMWy96tMiL8Yl7EFA">Tam Xuyên quan thuỷ trướng nhị thập vận - 三川觀水漲二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/T%E1%BB%B1-thu%E1%BA%A